				h1.ar-heading.rb-bg.f-oku.wtxt who is ROBONOBO?
				p.ar-text With ROBONOBO's constantly changing body and adapting brain, this cybernetic chimp is a fierce opponent for heroes and villain alike. With his phenominal robot AI, ROBONOBO is constantly refactoring and adjusting his own plans. This type of machine learning means you'll have access to a diverse toolkit capable of squaring off with any opponent.

				p.ar-text ROBONOBO is a defensive all-purpose charage that gives players a fair chance against most strategies. ROBONOBO's EVOLVE skill allows player to easily adjust their strategy via refresh their feats. Focused deckbuilders could even get to a point where they are playing a Feat during every turn of the game.
	
				p.ar-text Although ROBONOBO's skill requires players to monitor their Feats more often than other characters, he is still a great choice for a beginning player. As an EASY character, players will find that Robonobo offers powerful utilities and lots of synergy. ROBO may lack the explosive damage or combo potential that other characters possess, but makes up for that by being the most consistent character in the game.
		.row.ar-row
